      <section eId="sec_47_16_102">
        <num>47-16-102</num>
        <content>
          <p>In addition to the retirement benefits provided in this chapter, death benefits shall be paid to members in accordance with the following:</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1963, p. 630, § 19; Ga. L. 1974, p. 1191, § 1; Ga. L. 1978, p. 904, § 1; Ga. L. 1980, p. 768, § 1; Ga. L. 1981, p. 1853, § 2; Ga. L. 1981, p. 694, § 1; Ga. L. 1983, p. 3, § 36; Ga. L. 1983, p. 1185, § 6; Ga. L. 1985, p. 209, § 1; Ga. L. 1986, p. 607, § 1; Ga. L. 1994, p. 325, § 5; Ga. L. 2008, p. 132, § 1/HB 358; Ga. L. 2010, p. 1207, § 64/SB 436.)</p>
          <p>The 2008 amendment,
      effective July 1, 2008, substituted "$15,000.00" for "$7,000.00" twice in paragraph (2).</p>
          <p>The 2010 amendment,
      effective July 1, 2010, added "and" at the end of paragraph (3).</p>
        </content>
